     H            Y.
     F** AZZR12 *******************************************
     F* FROM ASCII TO EBCDIC CONVERSION SUBROUTINE *
     F* C: N.HAYAKAWA 86.09.11                            *
     F*****************************************************
     FGGAPP21 IT  F      36           EDISK
     E                    CD         30  1
     E    GGAPP21         TABC   18 256  1   TABD    1   ASCII
     C           *ENTRY    PLIST
     C                     PARM           EB     30
     C                     MOVEAEB        CD
     C                     Z-ADD1         J       20
     C           1         DO   30        J
     C                     MOVE CD,J      KEY     1
     C           KEY       LOKUPTABD      TABC           01
     C           *IN01     IFEQ '1'
     C                     MOVE TABC      CD,J
     C                     END
     C                     END
     C                     MOVEACD        EB
     C                     RETRN
